---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import CTABlock from '../../components/CTABlock.astro';
export const prerender = true;
---

<Layout
  title="Website Builds — From $240 | Fast Web Guru"
  description="Modern AI-editable websites built properly, reviewed by human specialists, and ready to update without a developer from day one. From $240 once-off."
>
  <section class="section-dark py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-white mb-6">A new website that actually makes the phone ring.</h1>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 text-xl leading-relaxed mb-8">Fast Web Guru builds modern, AI-editable websites — built properly, reviewed by human specialists, and set up to update without a developer from day one.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary text-base py-4 px-8">Talk to us about your website →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem -->
  <section class="section-warm py-16">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">"I paid $3,000 and haven't gotten a single lead."</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-text-secondary text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">It's the most common complaint in the Australian small business web market. And it's almost never about the money — it's about what came after. A website delivered, a developer who disappeared, no one to call when traffic comes but nobody converts.</p>
      <p class="text-brand-dark font-medium text-lg">Fast Web Guru builds websites differently.</p>
      <p class="text-brand-text-secondary text-lg leading-relaxed mt-3">Every build is reviewed by a human specialist — that's a hard internal rule, not a feature we added to sound good. We also install the same click-and-comment update system at launch, so the moment the site is live, you can update it without chasing anyone.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing -->
  <section class="section-light section-pad">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-12">
        <h2 class="mb-4">Clear prices. Every level of detail.</h2>
        <p class="text-brand-text-secondary text-lg">Every build is quoted based on what you need. The prices below are our typical ranges — we'll give you a straight answer after a short conversation.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-12 max-w-3xl">
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-6 text-brand-text-secondary uppercase text-sm tracking-widest">Standard Websites</h3>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            {[
              { price: '$240', desc: 'Up to 5 pages', note: 'Service businesses, landing pages' },
              { price: '$1,200', desc: 'Most business websites', note: 'Most common starting point' },
              { price: '$2,400', desc: 'Complex sites', note: 'Integrations or custom requirements' },
            ].map(row => (
              <div class="border-b border-brand-border pb-6">
                <div class="font-heading font-extrabold text-4xl text-brand-dark">{row.price}</div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-brand-dark mt-1">{row.desc}</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-brand-text-secondary">{row.note}</div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-6 text-brand-text-secondary uppercase text-sm tracking-widest">Ecommerce Sites</h3>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            {[
              { price: '$4,800', desc: 'New or migrating stores', note: 'Up to ~200 products' },
              { price: '$7,600', desc: 'Larger stores', note: 'Complex requirements' },
              { price: '$9,000', desc: 'Custom/complex', note: 'Scoped individually' },
            ].map(row => (
              <div class="border-b border-brand-border pb-6">
                <div class="font-heading font-extrabold text-4xl text-brand-dark">{row.price}</div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-brand-dark mt-1">{row.desc}</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-brand-text-secondary">{row.note}</div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="callout-box max-w-2xl">
        <p class="font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">The 20% rule</p>
        <p class="text-brand-text-secondary">On every build: at least 20% of the budget is allocated to a human specialist reviewing and refining the work. That's what stops a Fast Web Guru site from looking like a template.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What's included -->
  <section class="section-mid section-pad">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="mb-10">What's included in every build</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-5 list-none p-0">
        {[
          'Full-code website on modern infrastructure (not a template CMS)',
          'Click-and-comment update system installed from day one — same-day updates immediately at launch',
          'Mobile-first design, speed-optimised, security-hardened',
          'Full access to all files, hosting, and logins on delivery',
          'Hosted on Fast Web Guru infrastructure if joining a monthly plan',
        ].map(item => (
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5"/></svg>
            <span class="text-brand-dark text-lg">{item}</span>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Upsell to plans -->
  <section class="section-dark py-14">
    <div class="container max-w-2xl text-center">
      <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl text-white mb-4">A new website without someone looking after it is a shop with no staff.</h3>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 text-lg mb-8">We recommend pairing any build with a Core ($40/mo) or Advanced ($240/mo) plan so your investment keeps performing long after launch day.</p>
      <a href="/pricing" class="btn-inverse">See plans and pricing →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Final CTA -->
  <section class="section-light section-pad">
    <div class="container max-w-2xl text-center">
      <h2 class="mb-4">Not sure what you need?</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-text-secondary text-lg mb-8">Get a free AI assessment. We'll look at what you've got and tell you honestly — new build, migration, or upgrade — what would actually make the most difference.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/#assessment" class="btn-primary">Get Your Free AI Assessment</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-secondary">Or talk to us directly →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
